      "content": "- I also want to see you and your duo praticing together as this is key in a team gamemode mode for success you need ot know eachothers playstyles and play to those playstyles or make certain moves etc that best suit your team to win every fight and rotate smoothly etc. I now goes without saying you must have team roles one person is the guy who voice didicates where you guys roatate and has the final say. It is vital you guys stick together when playing in endgame especially and having one person making the calls will make this all much easier than \"co igling\" saving you time\n- If you want a training routine you can use https://discord.com/channels/971731167621574666/1426073254585696298/1467715808103759964",
